Quick Description
-----------------
A python wrapper for the shortboxed.com_ API.

.. _shortboxed.com: https://shortboxed.com/

Installation
------------

PyPi
~~~~

.. code:: bash

  $ pip3 install --user serifan

Example Usage
-------------
.. code-block:: python

    import serifan

    m = serifan.api()

    # Get this weeks comic releases.
    results = m.new_releases()

    # Print the results
    for i in results:
        print(f"{i.title}")

